---
---

<section class="section story" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story__inner">
      <div class="story__photo" role="img" aria-label="Photo of Adam Keif, owner and electrician">
        <img src="/assets/adam-keif-job-site.png" alt="Adam Keif" />
        <span class="story__photo-label">Adam Keif · San Luis Obispo, CA</span>
        <span class="story__photo-tag">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Owner-operated
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="story__content">
        <span class="eyebrow">Hi, I'm Adam.</span>
        <h2 id="about-title" class="story__title">
          Every job is done by <em>me</em>, personally.
        </h2>
        <div class="story__bio">
          <p>
            I started Keif Electric to prioritize care and craftsmanship. No surprises.
          </p>
          <p>
            No subs, no handoffs. When you hire Keif Electric, you hire me. I'm based in San Luis Obispo and I serve homeowners and builders across SLO County. The work gets done to code, on time, and at the price we agreed on.
          </p>
          <p>
            I keep the truck stocked, I pull the permits, I clean up after myself. If something doesn't sit right with you when I'm done, I'll come back and make it right.
          </p>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="story__quote">
          <p>The work gets done to code, on time, and at the price we agreed on. No subs, no surprises.</p>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="story__sign">
          <span class="story__sign-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span>Adam Keif, Owner · CA# 1152084</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: var(--ke-bone);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: var(--gutter);
    padding-right: var(--gutter);
  }

  .story__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story__photo {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    background: var(--ke-clay);
    border-radius: var(--radius-4);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-3);
  }

  .story__photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
  }

  .story__photo::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 35%, rgba(243, 152, 31, 0.25), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 60%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .story__photo-tag {
    position: absolute;
    right: 18px;
    top: 18px;
    z-index: 2;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: var(--ke-orange);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .story__photo-tag svg {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
  }

  .story__photo-label {
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    bottom: 20px;
    z-index: 2;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(246, 241, 232, 0.85);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
  }

  .story__content {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ke-orange);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--ke-orange);
  }

  .story__title {
    margin: 14px 0 22px;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 3.6vw, 50px);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--ke-ink);
  }

  .story__title em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--ke-orange);
  }

  .story__bio {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ke-ink);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .story__bio p {
    font-size: 17px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story__quote {
    margin: 32px 0 0;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    background: var(--ke-paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-3);
    position: relative;
  }

  .story__quote::before {
    content: '\201C';
    position: absolute;
    top: -22px;
    left: 18px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-variation-settings: 'YEAR' 2050;
    font-size: 80px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ke-orange);
  }

  .story__quote p {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ke-ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story__sign {
    margin-top: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .story__sign-line {
    width: 32px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--ke-orange);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .story__photo {
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 2;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
